TopicTitle: I'm at my wits end! Alien Space Program

Articles.Content: So I've been working on a version of Alien Space Program (originally by GregroxMun) on Minmus. I've pretty much finished moving the Mun and duplicating Kerbin. I just CAN'T GET THIS THING TO WORK AND IT'S liquidING ME OFF! Can someone EXTREMELY talented in Kopernicus and Module Manager please help!
